.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is used to make the NPC run away.  This will be
called by the combat code for wimpy when the NPC is bellow the
number of points used to trigger the wimpy action.
.EP

